  "subject": "Enable kafka consumer auto commit",
  "commit_message": "Enable kafka consumer auto commit\n\nIt appears that reactor-kafka is setting this property to false, which\nmakes our CSITs fail sometimes due to automatic reset of consumer offset.\n\nBy enabling auto-committing, Kafka broker should persist consumer offset.\n\nChange-Id: Ie4af7ef516dcde450cc31a499d82c5a90a0ad6c1\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-1495\nSigned-off-by: Filip Krzywka <filip.krzywka@nokia.com>\n",
